// Cloudflare
// https://developers.cloudflare.com/dns/zone-setups/partial-setup/setup/#3-add-dns-records
// Most of them are already in PSL. But in <X>.cdn.cloudflare.net, <X> itself is a domain.
// So we are stripping a second level of suffix here.
com.cdn.cloudflare.net
net.cdn.cloudflare.net
org.cdn.cloudflare.net
uk.cdn.cloudflare.net
rs.cdn.cloudflare.net
de.cdn.cloudflare.net
ru.cdn.cloudflare.net
fr.cdn.cloudflare.net
ca.cdn.cloudflare.net
es.cdn.cloudflare.net
gov.cdn.cloudflare.net